N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5006.10 - Agent compensation

State Regulations

The commission shall allow a compensation rate of six
percent for each ticket sold to an agent. The commission shall allow such
compensation by permitting an agent to deduct such compensation rate from the
face value otherwise payable by the agent to the commission. Notes
